Question: All images show pigs swimming across a natural body of water, all pigs swim in the same direction, and the left image contains more pigs than the right image.

Reference Answer: False

ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Does the image show pigs swimming across a natural body of water?')

ANSWER7=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER1} and {ANSWER3}')
ANSWER8=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER6} and {ANSWER7}')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER8)
